<template>
  <v-form>
    <v-container>
      <v-row>
        <v-col cols="12" sm="6" md="4">
          <v-text-field label="Search" solo dense v-model="message"></v-text-field>
          <v-btn @click="change()">submit</v-btn>

        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>

  </v-form>

</template>
<script>
import axios from 'axios';


export default {

  data: () => {
    return {}

  },
  methods: () => ({
    async change(){
      await axios.post(`http://127.0.0.1:40193/search`,{
        Key: this.message
      }).then(resposne=>{
        this.$emit()
      })
    }

  })

}
</script>
